  "bio": [
    "Robin Zeng is the founder and chairman of Contemporary Amperex Technology (CATL),  one of the world's largest suppliers of batteries for electric vehicles.",
    "CATL, which listed on the Shenzhen Stock Exchange in 2018, supplies batteries to such automakers as BMW, Volkswagen and Geely.",
    "CATL is headquartered in Zeng's hometown of Ningde in Fujian Province.",
    "The company has been working with Ford since 2023 to build a battery factory in Michigan, although the original $3.5 billion plant has been downsized amid geopolitical tensions."
  ],
  "about": [
    "Zeng worked at a state-owned shipbuilding company in Fujian Province early in his career."
  ]
